LLM_response:
要在图像中确定文字的位置，我们可以选择左键单击图像的中心部位。基于图像像素尺寸为 800x800，中心位置大约在宽度的400像素和高度的400像素处。以下动作将模拟在图片中心点击以确定文本位置的操作：

```json
[
    {"action_type":"MouseAction","mouse_action_type":"click","mouse_button":"left","mouse_position":{"width":400,"height":400}}
]
```

LLM_response_editer_en:
To determine the position of the text in the image, we can use the mouse to operate.```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "move", "mouse_position": {"width": 454, "height": 172}},
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "drag", "mouse_button": "left", "mouse_position": {"width": 564, "height": 203}}
]
```
